<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Roth Conversion Strategy — {{ firm_name }}</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bronze: #867550;
    --bronze-dark: #6b5d3f;
    --ink: #232020;
    --charcoal: #32373c;
    --paper: #f5f5f5;
    --rule: #d9d4c7;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; }

  html, body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: 'Poppins', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: #e9e6df;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .page {
    width: 8.5in;
    min-height: 11in;
    margin: 24px auto;
    background: var(--paper);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .masthead {
    background: #000;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 28px 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--bronze);
  }

  .mark { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px; }
  .mark svg { width: 44px; height: 52px; }

  .wordmark {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 15px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .wordmark span {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--bronze);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .doc-label {
    text-align: right;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bronze);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .doc-label strong {
    display: block;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .client-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    padding: 18px 48px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    background: #fff;
  }
  .client-strip .cell { font-size: 11px; }
  .client-strip .cell .label {
    color: var(--bronze);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 9px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .client-strip .cell .value {
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .recommendation {
    padding: 36px 48px 28px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .eyebrow {
    color: var(--bronze);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .headline {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    max-width: 640px;
  }
  .headline .amount { color: var(--bronze); font-weight: 600; }
  .rationale {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 620px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .signature {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    padding: 32px 48px;
    background: #fff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .signature .lever-label {
    color: var(--bronze);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .signature .lever-copy {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .signature .big { text-align: right; }
  .signature .big .number {
    font-size: 56px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bronze);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .signature .big .caption {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-top: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .schedule { padding: 28px 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bronze);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    margin: 0 0 14px 0;
  }

  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12px; }
  thead th {
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--bronze);
    background: #fafaf7;
  }
  thead th:nth-child(n+3) { text-align: right; }
  tbody td { padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); font-weight: 400; }
  tbody td:nth-child(n+3) { text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  tbody tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  tbody td.convert-amount { font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); }

  .schedule-total {
    margin-top: 12px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .schedule-total .total-value {
    color: var(--bronze);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-transform: none;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .tradeoff {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    padding: 28px 48px;
    gap: 40px;
    background: #fff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .tradeoff .col h3 {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: var(--bronze);
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
  }
  .tradeoff .col p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .tradeoff .col p strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }

  .foot {
    padding: 22px 48px 28px;
    margin-top: auto;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--bronze);
    background: #000;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .foot .advisor-line {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    font-size: 11px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .foot .advisor-line strong {
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 10px;
  }
  .foot .advisor-line span { color: var(--bronze); }
  .disclosure {
    font-size: 8.5px;
    color: #9a9388;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  @media print {
    body { background: #fff; }
    .page { margin: 0; box-shadow: none; }
    @page { size: letter; margin: 0; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="page">

  <header class="masthead">
    <div class="mark">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 100 120" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
        <rect x="6" y="4" width="88" height="10" fill="#867550"/>
        <path d="M 10 22 L 10 68 Q 10 98 50 114 Q 90 98 90 68 L 90 22 Z"
              fill="none" stroke="#867550" stroke-width="4.5"/>
        <text x="50" y="72" text-anchor="middle"
              font-family="Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif"
              font-size="46" font-weight="400" fill="#867550">R</text>
        <rect x="42" y="80" width="16" height="2.5" fill="#867550"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="wordmark">
        {{ firm_name_line_1 }}<br>{{ firm_name_line_2 }}
        <span>{{ firm_tagline }}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="doc-label">
      <strong>{{ report_date }}</strong>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="recommendation">
    <div class="eyebrow">Our Recommendation</div>
    <h1 class="headline">
      Convert <span class="amount">{{ total_conversion_usd | currency_exact }}</span> from your Traditional IRA to a Roth IRA over the next {{ conversion_years_count_word }} years.
    </h1>
    <p class="rationale">
      You have a window right now — {% if is_mfj %}both retired, married filing jointly{% else %}retired, filing single{% endif %}, in the {{ current_bracket_display }} bracket. We use it deliberately. The real risk is not today&rsquo;s tax bill; it&rsquo;s what happens to the surviving spouse when filing status changes from joint to single.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="signature">
    <div class="lever">
      <div class="lever-label">Why This Matters</div>
      <p class="lever-copy">
        When one spouse passes, the survivor files as <strong>single</strong> &mdash; where the same income hits the {{ survivor_single_bracket_range_display }} brackets <em>much</em> sooner. Your current Required Minimum Distributions would push the surviving spouse into a tax bracket spike for the rest of their life. This plan reduces the IRA balance now so that spike is absorbed, not inherited.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="big">
      <div class="number">{{ lifetime_tax_saved_usd | currency_approx }}</div>
      <div class="caption">Est. Additional Lifetime Tax<br>the Surviving Spouse Would Face</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="schedule">
    <h2 class="section-title">Your {{ conversion_years_count_word_title }}-Year Conversion Schedule</h2>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="width: 12%;">Year</th>
          <th style="width: 16%;">{{ age_column_header }}</th>
          <th style="width: 24%;">Conversion</th>
          <th style="width: 24%;">Top Marginal Bracket</th>
          <th style="width: 24%;">Medicare IRMAA Tier</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for row in schedule_rows %}
        <tr>
          <td>{{ row.year }}</td>
          <td>{{ row.age_display }}</td>
          <td class="convert-amount">{{ row.conversion_usd | currency_exact }}</td>
          <td>{{ row.bracket_pct | pct }}</td>
          <td>{{ row.irmaa_tier_mult | irmaa_tier }}</td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <div class="schedule-total">
      <span>Total Converted Before RMD Escalation</span>
      <span class="total-value">{{ total_conversion_usd | currency_exact }}</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="tradeoff">
    <div class="col">
      <h3>What It Costs</h3>
      <p>
        An additional <strong>{{ first_year_conversion_tax_usd | currency_approx }}</strong> in federal tax per conversion year, and a Medicare premium increase of roughly <strong>{{ annual_medicare_irmaa_usd | currency_approx_no_tilde }}/year</strong> in the years income is reported at this level.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <h3>What It Preserves</h3>
      <p>
        An estimated <strong>{{ lifetime_tax_saved_usd | currency_approx_no_tilde }}</strong> in lifetime tax the surviving spouse would otherwise pay, a lower RMD stream once they&rsquo;re filing single, and a larger Roth balance that passes to heirs tax-free.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="foot">
    <div class="advisor-line">
      <strong>{{ firm_name }}</strong>
      <span>{{ firm_website }}</span>
    </div>
    <p class="disclosure">
      {{ disclosure_text }}{% for note in extra_disclosure_notes %} {{ note }}{% endfor %}
    </p>
  </footer>

</div>

</body>
</html>
